data.description: Home Sweet Home includes over 2.5 acres with an attached 2 car garage. Along with a 4 car garage including drive through doors and drop down staircase to attic space. 2 oversized heavy duty RV parking structures with plenty of concrete to keep all your treasures clean and protected. The pool and jacuzzi has concrete block wall for privacy and will block the wind with a quaint pergola for all your pool parties. Entire property fenced and electric gate for easy access. Mature trees throughout and newly painted exterior along with your own private patio off the huge Family room and beautiful back yard. The home is well maintained with walk in pantry and custom bar in Family room. Close to shopping and commuting making it the perfect ranch with city amenities. Peace and tranquility throughout your perfect new home.
